# Final check for isolated entities:
# All Agents are linked via management or roles.
# All ProductModels are linked to Resources.
# All Locations are linked to Sites/Rooms and Resources.
# All Resources are linked to Agents, ProductModels, Locations, NetworkInterfaces, Applications, and potentially other Resources (clusterController).
# All NetworkInterfaces are linked to Resources and NetworkLinks.
# All NetworkLinks are linked to Agents, Resources, and NetworkInterfaces.
# All Applications are linked to Resources, ApplicationModules, and Agents.
# All ApplicationModules are linked to Applications, Agents, and Services.
# All Services are linked to ApplicationModules/Applications/Resources.
# All EventRecords are linked to ManagedObjects, ManagementSystems, and potentially Agents.
# All TroubleTickets are linked to Services/Applications/Resources, Agents, EventRecords, and Notes.
# All TroubleTicketNotes are linked to TroubleTickets, Agents, and potentially EventRecords.
# All ChangeRequests are linked to Applications/Resources, Agents, and potentially EventRecords.
# All OperationPlans are linked to Pre/Post Conditions.
# All ActionPre/PostConditions are linked to OperationPlans.
# All DocumentAttachments are linked to TroubleTickets/ChangeRequests.

# The graph is dense and connected.
